                </TextBlock>
            </StackPanel>
            <StackPanel x:Key="TableEditToolTip">
                <TextBlock>
				Allows scripting &amp; editing of database tables used to support the Virtual Expert.
                </TextBlock>
            </StackPanel>
            <StackPanel x:Key="UserManagementToolTip">
                <TextBlock>
				Use with causion!
                </TextBlock>
            </StackPanel>
            <StackPanel x:Key="EnableLanguageInheritanceToolTip">
