				When enabled (highlighted with green tick), this feature will allow inheritance of text changes in different languages that do not already have alternative text defined for each field.
                </TextBlock>
                <Rectangle Height="1" HorizontalAlignment="Stretch" Stroke="Blue" Margin="0,6,0,6" StrokeThickness="1" />
